Age development and Reliability

knit_text <- \(text, ...) knitr::knit(text = text, ...)
for (row in seq_len(nrow(games_included))) {
  cur_game_info <- slice(games_included, row)
  knitr::knit_expand(rmd_child_check_index) |> 
    knit_text(quiet = TRUE) |> 
    cat()
  cat("\n\n")
}

Basic Information

targets::tar_read_raw(
  str_glue("indices_clean_{cur_game_info$game_name_abbr}")
) %>%
  group_by(index) %>%
  group_modify(
    ~ .x %>%
      summarise(
        N_Total = n(),
        N_Invalid = sum(is.na(is_valid) | !is_valid),
        N_Outlier = sum(!is.na(is_valid) & is_valid & is_outlier)
      )
  ) %>%
  ungroup() %>%
  gt(rowname_col = "index") %>%
  tab_stubhead(label = "Index Name") %>%
  tab_spanner_delim(delim = "_") %>%
  tab_options(column_labels.font.weight = "bold")
